                  p Apple or Android? Coke or vitaminwater? Today's consumers often define themselves through brand choices. How can business leaders navigate this fast-changing landscape in a media age that's characterized by capricious loyalties and nanosecond attention spans? For a company to succeed, behind edgy new branding should be a promise to deliver value and to stand up at every "customer touch point."
